Eucalyptus Version: {{4.2.0-0.0.23586.540.20150623git1ad8a4a.el6}}

*Steps*

# Set up four individual clouds (2 x multi-cluster, 2 x single cluster)
#* [cloud-466 | http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/Quick%20Launch%20Master/466/]
#* [cloud-465 | http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/Quick%20Launch%20Master/465/]
