#* [cloud-463 | http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/Quick%20Launch%20Master/463/]
# Enabled Eucalyptus DNS on all four clouds
# Downloaded and sourced eucalyptus/admin user credentials for each cloud
# Set {{region.region_name}} locally on each cloud
#* {code}euctl region.region_name=ace-hood --region @localhost{code}
#* {code}euctl region.region_name=big-krit --region @localhost{code}
#* {code}euctl region.region_name=bob --region @localhost{code}
#* {code}euctl region.region_name=ghostface-killah --region @localhost{code}
# Set {{region.region_ssl_verify_hostnames}} to false locally on each cloud
#* {code}euctl region.region_ssl_verify_hostnames=false --region @localhost{code}
# Created the following region config, and uploaded configuration to {{region.region_configuration}} on each cloud
